### Paisadu Data Extractor API Endpoints Test File

### Health Check / Info Endpoint
GET http://localhost:5001/api
Accept: application/json


### Export Edited Rows to Excel
POST http://localhost:5001/api/export/excel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rows": [
    {
      "pageNumber": 1,
      "rowNumber": 1,
      "city": "BANGALORE",
      "phoneNumber": "+91-9845012345",
      "amount": 45000,
      "originalOcrText": "PRP-001 | TechPark Towers BANGALORE PINCODE | MOBILE: +91-9845012345 | 45000",
      "confidence": 98,
      "needsReview": false
    },
    {
      "pageNumber": 2,
      "rowNumber": 2,
      "city": "HYDERABAD",
      "phoneNumber": "040-23456789",
      "amount": 62500,
      "originalOcrText": "PRP-002 | Banjara Hills Heights HYDERABAD PINCODE | PHONE: 040-23456789 | 62500",
      "confidence": 85,
      "needsReview": true
    }
  ],
  "includeOcrText": true
}


